30#ifndef _DMU_SEND_H
31#define _DMU_SEND_H
32
33#include <sys/spa.h>
34
35struct vnode;
36struct dsl_dataset;
37struct drr_begin;
38struct avl_tree;
39struct dmu_replay_record;
40
41extern const char *recv_clone_name;
42
43int dmu_send(const char *tosnap, const char *fromsnap, boolean_t embedok,
44 boolean_t large_block_ok, int outfd, uint64_t resumeobj, uint64_t resumeoff,
45#ifdef illumos
46 struct vnode *vp, offset_t *off);
47#else
48 struct file *fp, offset_t *off);
49#endif
50int dmu_send_estimate(struct dsl_dataset *ds, struct dsl_dataset *fromds,
51 uint64_t *sizep);
52int dmu_send_estimate_from_txg(struct dsl_dataset *ds, uint64_t fromtxg,
53 uint64_t *sizep);
54int dmu_send_obj(const char *pool, uint64_t tosnap, uint64_t fromsnap,
55 boolean_t embedok, boolean_t large_block_ok,
56#ifdef illumos
57 int outfd, struct vnode *vp, offset_t *off);
58#else
59 int outfd, struct file *fp, offset_t *off);
60#endif
61
62typedef struct dmu_recv_cookie {
63 struct dsl_dataset *drc_ds;
64 struct dmu_replay_record *drc_drr_begin;
65 struct drr_begin *drc_drrb;
66 const char *drc_tofs;
67 const char *drc_tosnap;
68 boolean_t drc_newfs;
69 boolean_t drc_byteswap;
70 boolean_t drc_force;
71 boolean_t drc_resumable;
72 struct avl_tree *drc_guid_to_ds_map;
73 zio_cksum_t drc_cksum;
74 uint64_t drc_newsnapobj;
75 void *drc_owner;
76 cred_t *drc_cred;
77} dmu_recv_cookie_t;
78
79int dmu_recv_begin(char *tofs, char *tosnap,
80 struct dmu_replay_record *drr_begin,
81 boolean_t force, boolean_t resumable, char *origin, dmu_recv_cookie_t *drc);
82#ifdef illumos
83int dmu_recv_stream(dmu_recv_cookie_t *drc, struct vnode *vp, offset_t *voffp,
84#else
85int dmu_recv_stream(dmu_recv_cookie_t *drc, struct file *fp, offset_t *voffp,
86#endif
87 int cleanup_fd, uint64_t *action_handlep);
88int dmu_recv_end(dmu_recv_cookie_t *drc, void *owner);
89boolean_t dmu_objset_is_receiving(objset_t *os);
90
91#endif /* _DMU_SEND_H */
